{"title":"雪山上升起太阳","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":5,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山上升起太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳从东方升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山上映出万道金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像毛主席在问我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“生活过的怎么样？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知道怎样回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有请他老人家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看看我们脸上的红光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵树上三枝桠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三枝桠上三朵花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵献给蓝天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的恩情比蓝天还高；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵献给岩石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的领导比岩石还坚强；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一朵献给江水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏、汉人民的情谊比江水还长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党领导我们打开了幸福之门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族人民得到彻底解放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像雪山上升起了太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛苦的生活雪化冰消。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主改革推翻了旧制度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族人民得到了新生活。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像天空的霹雳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶的农奴主低头了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"×××"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用木碗舀水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子也舀不干。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用木犁耕地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远也提不高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细小的水流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇成了滔滔的澜沧江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走合作化的道路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美好的希望就能实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"康巴民歌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}